 - CodeInterpreter not found\n- [ ] Test 500 Internal Server Error cases:\n  - Store connection failure\n  - K8s API error\n  - Timeout scenarios\n- [ ] Verify error messages match specification\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v -run \"TestHandle.*Error\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 18: Integration Test - Successful Creation Flow\n**Verifiable Output:** End-to-end test passes\n\n- [ ] Create integration test file\n- [ ] Test complete flow:\n  1. Create test AgentRuntime in fake clientset\n  2. POST /v1/agent-runtime with valid request\n  3. Mock SandboxReconciler to signal running\n  4. Verify 200 response with sessionId\n  5. Verify Store contains sandbox record\n  6. Verify response includes entryPoints\n- [ ] Test same flow for CodeInterpreter\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v -run \"TestIntegration.*Create\" -tags=integration\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 19: Integration Test - Timeout and Rollback\n**Verifiable Output:** Timeout scenario tested\n\n- [ ] Test timeout scenario:\n  1. Create valid request\n  2. Don't signal running from reconciler\n  3. Verify timeout after 2 minutes\n  4. Verify CR is deleted\n  5. Verify Store record is cleaned up\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v -run \"TestIntegration.*Timeout\" -tags=integration\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 20: Verify Test Coverage\n**Verifiable Output:** Coverage meets targets\n\n- [ ] Run tests with coverage: `go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`\n- [ ] Verify handler coverage >= 80%\n- [ ] Verify service/creator coverage >= 80%\n- [ ] Verify builder coverage >= 80%\n- [ ] Generate coverage report\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\ngo test -race -v -coverprofile=coverage.out -coverpkg=./pkg/workloadmanager/... ./pkg/workloadmanager/...\ngo tool cover -func=coverage.out | grep -E \"(handler|creator|builder)\" | awk '{sum+=$3; count++} END {print \"Avg coverage:\", sum/count